{"tid":1224114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子時代廣場內墮樓昏迷","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T16:02:36.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8a8c891302f34665ad26bcdecd089101eeb7d6","tid":1224114,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:07:08.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣時代廣場，今早8時43分，一名中年男子被發現在商場內高處墮下，重傷倒卧中庭位置，陷入昏迷，救護員接報到場，將男子送院搶救，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n有在時代廣場工作的讀者表示，事發時突然聽到一聲巨響，於是前往查看，驚見男子倒卧在地上。他指過往亦曾遇過同類事件，今次已是自己第3次遇見，坦言感到害怕，亦不敢上前查看。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=3dc82af2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190615/59717638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59717638&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=83d9bb4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59717638&h=1ef96849\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190615/59717638</a>"},{"pid":"ade6b3923c91a08de10225a0e686a4463247559c","tid":1224114,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後政府同你講香港仲係好成功"},{"pid":"b21733cb3aed562f9a52cc16e8912087ef4a1ab4","tid":1224114,"uid":128117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:01:43.000Z","msg":"一日跳兩件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor